{"tid":1803029,"cid":5,"subCid":10,"title":"修例風波：紀念逝者十字架疑遭港人破壞　立陶宛外交部調查","createTime":"2019-12-30T01:54:20.000Z","updateTime":"2019-12-31T04:36:21.000Z","uid":308287,"like":4,"dislike":6,"uniUserReply":12,"replies":[{"pid":"67e837319a0a715c3dd124c77fa6b9ae25eba021","tid":1803029,"uid":308287,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-12-30T01:54:20.000Z","msg":"<strong><span style=\"font-size: x-large;\">手足們，寫還寫都要睇情況先好寫呀！<img src=\"/assets/faces/big/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n唔係嘅話會令國際反感架啦！<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/dead.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /></span></strong><br />\n<br />\n<br />\n<a href=\"https://hk.on.cc/hk/bkn/cnt/news/20191229/mobile/bkn-20191229221135943-1229_00822_001.html\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fhk.on.cc%2Fhk%2Fbkn%2Fcnt%2Fnews%2F20191229%2Fmobile%2Fbkn-20191229221135943-1229_00822_001.html&d=LK0Ahc5Iz%2F4EhQQuEN3KkdlAIsOV5GGnQ0mU6qdzh4w%3D&h=e2d40b97\" target=\"_blank\">https://hk.on.cc/hk/bkn/cnt/news/20191229/mobile/bkn-20191229221135943-1229_00822_001.html</a><br />\n<br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/kfbMbjO.png\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FkfbMbjO.png&h=7087a4c8&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<br />\n連月反修例示威令香港社會動盪不止，而目前有關爭議更傳至海外！中文大學新聞與傳播學院客席講師梁啟智日前到訪立陶宛十字架山，發現有人將當地寫上支持香港抗爭的十字架遭到塗污，更有一個紀念逝者的十字架上，被寫上「願曱甴早日安息，願香港早日回復平靜」的字句。梁認為有關行為對當地歷史等方面大為不敬，感到憤怒。立陶宛外交部長Linas Linkevicius亦就事件在twitter發出聲明指，有關破壞行為非常可恥且不能容忍，目前當局正就事件調查。<br />\n<br />\n梁啟智在其Facebook專頁表示，若其他人有意見可以自行購買十字架再寫上意見，但在一個紀念先人的十字架寫上有關字句，是對先人大不敬；而十字架山是紀念立陶宛人的反抗歷史，但有人將對香港抗爭者的仇恨帶到這兒，並在十字架上寫上仇恨言論是對宗教、這段歷史和抗爭精神的大不敬。<br />\n梁又指，由於十字架山屬宗教聖地，紀念着的抗爭歷史，向來有不少人架設寫上政治訴求的十字架，近半年就有不少寫上「光復香港 時代革命」的字句。<br />\n<br />\n另外，網上亦有影片流傳一名操流利國語女士，將一個寫有「光復香港 時代革命」字句的十字架丢棄。立陶宛外交部長Linas Linkevicius今日就事件在twitter回應，就有關行為感羞恥，並強調會作調查。"},{"pid":"40b6c74179e33cbc154fc419ffc1559adf98ca5c","tid":1803029,"uid":149494,"like":6,"dislike":0,"score":6,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-12-30T02:00:35.000Z","msg":"關手足們咩事？<br />\n屌緊藍屍喎"},{"pid":"ec65960a8615b697e61a0568cd3caa7ba663f121","tid":1803029,"uid":51271,"like":3,"dislike":0,"score":3,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-12-30T02:02:47.000Z","msg":"遭港人破壞 <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n<br />\n東方又點知係香港人劃花 <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"786ea7b34c5edaae0e061bb30cda0c675db444f7","tid":1803029,"uid":308287,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"40b6c74179e33cbc154fc419ffc1559adf98ca5c","tid":1803029,"uid":149494,"like":6,"dislike":0,"score":6,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-12-30T02:00:35.000Z","msg":"關手足們咩事？<br />\n屌緊藍屍喎"},"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-12-30T02:17:23.000Z","msg":"圖片右手邊個格。"},{"pid":"8226bc17d49ff9caabeed8c12854b6e73c8a99cb","tid":1803029,"uid":51158,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"quote":{"pid":"ec65960a8615b697e61a0568cd3caa7ba663f121","tid":1803029,"uid":51271,"like":3,"dislike":0,"score":3,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-12-30T02:02:47.000Z","msg":"遭港人破壞 <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n<br />\n東方又點知係香港人劃花 <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-12-30T02:46:30.000Z","msg":"理西佢，制裁香港啦<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/agree.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n連藍絲同埋蝗西都出手，黎攬炒啦"},{"pid":"18010344fb76d2771da7a219518bf7085ac864e8","tid":1803029,"uid":60977,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-12-30T02:49:33.000Z","msg":"有必要教一教中世紀波蘭立陶宛"},{"pid":"2c0cde86270e1f84a5da79db0f9497fb7fc22382","tid":1803029,"uid":268481,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-12-30T03:11:04.000Z","msg":"遭港人破壞<img src=\"/assets/faces/dogxm/haha.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n東方<img src=\"/assets/faces/dogxm/haha.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"16d91f29824f2712fbd85bede173b24db13f4661","tid":1803029,"uid":78392,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-12-30T03:20:06.000Z","msg":"Hi五毛<img src=\"/assets/faces/nor